general.desc: Hoang Huy Investment Services JSC is a Vietnam based company engaged in the business of manufacturing and importing medium and heavy trucks with DONGFENG brand - HO BAC. It is also involved in investing in large-scale real estate projects. The products offered by the company covers tractor truck, 3-foot ben cart, Ben8 ton truck, 4-legged truck, 2-foot barrel truck, trucks 5-foot container, concrete mixing car, and specialized vehicles.
general.short_desc: Hoang Huy Investment Services JSC is engaged in providing several business services which include business of the real-estate, right to the land using belonging to the owner, using owner or hiring; Retailing, wholesale of cars etc.
